дёӘжҺҘеҸЈпјҢFeign дјҡиҮӘеҠЁеё®дҪ еҸ‘йҖҒ HTTP иҜ·жұӮгҖӮ\n *\n * дёәд»Җд№ҲиҰҒз”Ё Feignпјҹ","truncated":false},"title":"beibu-mall/mall-product/mall-product-api/src/main/java/com/beibu/mall/product/api/feign/ProductFeignClient.java","tool_input":"{\"filePath\":\"/home/administrator/BeibuMall/beibu-mall/mall-product/mall-product-api/src/main/java/com/beibu/mall/product/api/feign/ProductFeignClient.java\"}","tool_name":"read","tool_output":"<path>/home/administrator/BeibuMall/beibu-mall/mall-product/mall-product-api/src/main/java/com/beibu/mall/product/api/feign/ProductFeignClient.java</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package com.beibu.mall.product.api.feign;\n2: \n3: import com.beibu.mall.common.result.Result;\n4: import com.beibu.mall.product.api.dto.SpuDetailVO;\n5: import com.beibu.mall.product.api.dto.SkuVO;\n6: import org.springframework.cloud.openfeign.FeignClient;\n7: import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.GetMapping;\n8: import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.PathVariable;\n9: import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RequestParam;\n10: \n11: import java.util.List;\n12: \n13: /**\n14:  * е•Ҷе“ҒжңҚеҠЎ Feign е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n15:  *\n16:  * д»Җд№ҲжҳҜ Feignпјҹ\n17:  * Feign жҳҜ Spring Cloud жҸҗдҫӣзҡ„еЈ°жҳҺејҸ HTTP е®ўжҲ·з«ҜгҖӮ\n18:  * дҪ еҸӘйңҖиҰҒе®ҡд№үдёҖдёӘжҺҘеҸЈпјҢFeign дјҡиҮӘеҠЁеё®дҪ еҸ‘йҖҒ HTTP иҜ·жұӮгҖӮ\n19:  *\n20:  * дёәд»Җд№ҲиҰҒз”Ё Feignпјҹ\n21:  * еңЁеҫ®жңҚеҠЎжһ¶жһ„дёӯпјҢжңҚеҠЎд№Ӣй—ҙйңҖиҰҒзӣёдә’и°ғз”ЁгҖӮ\n22:  * дҫӢеҰӮпјҡи®ўеҚ•жңҚеҠЎйңҖиҰҒжҹҘиҜўе•Ҷе“ҒдҝЎжҒҜпјҢе°ұйңҖиҰҒи°ғз”Ёе•Ҷе“ҒжңҚеҠЎзҡ„жҺҘеҸЈгҖӮ\n23:  * з”Ё Feign еҸҜд»ҘеғҸи°ғз”Ёжң¬ең°ж–№жі•дёҖж ·и°ғз”ЁиҝңзЁӢжңҚеҠЎгҖӮ\n24:  *\n25:  * @FeignClient жіЁи§ЈеҸӮж•°пјҡ\n26:  * - name: иҰҒи°ғз”Ёзҡ„жңҚеҠЎеҗҚз§°пјҲеңЁ Nacos дёӯжіЁеҶҢзҡ„еҗҚз§°пјү\n27:  * - path: URL еүҚзјҖ\n28:  *\n29:  * е…¶д»–жңҚеҠЎдҪҝз”Ёж–№ејҸпјҡ\n30:  * 1. еңЁ pom.xml дёӯдҫқиө– mall-product-api\n31:  * 2. еңЁеҗҜеҠЁзұ»дёҠж·»еҠ  @EnableFeignClients\n32:  * 3. жіЁе…Ҙ ProductFeignClient еҚіеҸҜдҪҝз”Ё\n33:  */\n34: @FeignClient(name = \"product-service\", path = \"/api/product\",\n35:     fallbackFactory = ProductFeignClientFallbackFactory.class)\n36: public interface ProductFeignClient {\n37: \n38:     /**\n39:      * жҹҘиҜўе•Ҷе“ҒиҜҰжғ…пјҲеҗ« SKU еҲ—иЎЁпјү\n40:      *\n41:      * и®ўеҚ•жңҚеҠЎдёӢеҚ•ж—¶йңҖиҰҒи°ғз”ЁжӯӨжҺҘеҸЈпјҢиҺ·еҸ–е•Ҷе“Ғд»·ж јгҖҒеә“еӯҳзӯүдҝЎжҒҜгҖӮ\n42:      */\n43:     @GetMapping(\"/spu/{id}\")\n44:     Result<SpuDetailVO> getSpuDetail(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long spuId);\n45: \n46:     /**\n47:      * ж №жҚ® SKU ID жҹҘиҜўеҚ•дёӘ SKU\n48:      * иҙӯзү©иҪҰжңҚеҠЎи°ғз”ЁжӯӨжҺҘеҸЈиҺ·еҸ–е•Ҷе“ҒеҗҚз§°гҖҒд»·ж јгҖҒеӣҫзүҮзӯүдҝЎжҒҜ\n49:      */\n50:     @GetMapping(\"/sku/{id}\")\n51:     Result<SkuVO> getSkuById(@PathVariable(\"id\") Long skuId);\n52: \n53:     /**\n54:      * жҹҘиҜў SPU дёӢзҡ„жүҖжңү SKU\n55:      */\n56:     @GetMapping(\"/sku/list\")\n57:     Result<List<SkuVO>> listSkuBySpuId(@RequestParam(\"spuId\") Long spuId);\n58: }\n\n(End of file - total 58 lines)\n</content>"},"sessionId":"ses_171455795ffeo63B76Yp50e4TY","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:24:32.916Z","toolInput":"{\"filePath\":\"/home/administrator/BeibuMall/beibu-mall/mall-product/mall-product-api/src/main/java/com/beibu/mall/product/api/feign/ProductFeignClient.java\"}","toolName":"read","toolOutput":"<path>/home/administrator/BeibuMall/beibu-mall/mall-product/mall-product-api/src/main/java/com/beibu/mall/product/api/feign/ProductFeignClient.java</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package com.beibu.mall.product.api.feign;\n2: \n3: import com.beibu.mall.common.result.Result;\n4: import com.beibu.mall.product.api.dto.SpuDetailVO;\n5: import com.beibu.mall.product.api.dto.SkuVO;\n6: import org.springframework.cloud.openfeign.FeignClient;\n7: import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.GetMapping;\n8: import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.PathVariable;\n9: import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RequestParam;\n10: \n11: import java.util.List;\n12: \n13: /**\n14:  * е•Ҷе“ҒжңҚеҠЎ Feign е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ